Decisions on Petitions for .Writs of Certiorari from February 24, to June 1, 1909.

No. 720. Bernarr Macfadden, Petitioner, v. The United States. March 1, 1909. Mr. Henry M. Earle for petitioner. The Solicitor General for respondent.

Petition for a writ of certiorari to the United States Circuit Court of Appeals for the Third Circuit denied.
